{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place pecorino in mixing bowl and grate <b>15 sec\/speed 10<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place onions and garlic in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then add olive oil and sauté <b>5 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add carrots and celery then chop <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b>.","Add mushrooms, tomatoes, tomato purée, bay leaves, rosemary, thyme, paprika, sugar, salt and pepper. Place Varoma dish into position then weigh in courgettes, ensuring some holes remain unobstructed for steam to circulate. Steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 1<b>.","Set Varoma aside. Remove rosemary, thyme and bay leaves from bolognese then season to taste.","Divide steamed courgette noodles between 4 bowls, ladle bolognese over each and sprinkle with reserved grated pecorino. Serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["100 g pecorino cheese, cut in pieces (3 cm)","110 g onions, quartered","2 garlic cloves","60 g olive oil","200 g carrots, sliced (1 cm)","2 celery stalks, cut in pieces","500 g fresh oyster mushrooms, cut in pieces","400 g tinned chopped tomatoes","30 g tomato purée","2 fresh bay leaves","1 sprig fresh rosemary","4 sprigs fresh thyme","2 tsp sweet paprika","2 tsp caster sugar","2 tsp fine sea salt, plus extra for seasoning","½ tsp ground black pepper, plus extra for seasoning","800 g courgettes, in thin strips (similar to ribbon noodles, see tip)"]}],"id":"r177754","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-HZWnuy1ncjI\/XZVQ-CNs5vI\/AAAAAAAAdIE\/0KxJtTe9ZscGdaA6FRThaElM4V-O82hEACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_biz0XOTvFPYpyAAZ.png","title":"Mushroom Bolognese with Courgette Noodles","publishedAt":"2017-07-31T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"20 g","fat":"24 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"22 g","calories":"1723 kJ \/ 412 kcal"},"basicInfo":["medium","20m","50m","4 portions"]}